700894f-b.title: Bronx: Gun Hill Road (East) - Barnes Avenue
700894f-b.text:
E. Gunhill Road, south side, east from Barnes to Bronxwood
Avenues, showing Evander Childs High School. The view is eastward
across Italian gardens from Tilden Street.
May 11, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, from a slightly different angle.
May 11, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
